                    <span>This book is the best one to get, whether you're a beginner or an old pro, it tells you everything you need to know, not just about mixing the drinks, but what you need to stock your own bar, the equipment, and the glassware. If you're looking for a guide to bartending, this is the one to get.</span>
                  
