                    <span>This book has tons of drinks and recipes. Tells you how to make exotic drinks , nonalchoholic drinks, low calorie drinks and many more. It also gives handy tips on how to toast , throw a party, even the proper way to pop champagne. Has 100's of good recipes and is very informative. Recomended.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Definately should be spiral bound</div>
