                    </div>
                    <span>Like others, I too would agree that this book should be spiral bound. It is rather difficult to mix a drink and try keep the book open. Even with that said, this is a great book with tons of recipies! Before I bought this book I didn't know how to make any mixed drinks and now I do. This book is not only great for bartenders, but anyone who likes to drink or have friends over for a night of fun. I highly recommend this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">VERY USER -FRIENDLY!!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
